The paper discusses the use of Artificial Immune Systems (AIS) in computational domains, which involves the use of algorithms inspired by the human immune system. This topic is closely related to the fields of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), control systems (cs.SY), and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
